ComicInfo.Title: I do, I do
ComicInfo.Summary:
Another full-color surprise from the infamous Rebecca. Guess who just got out of jail? Must be Stephanie for her bold break out in the last issue. After being in prison she just can’t help herself for being horny as hell – and boy does she want it bad. First on her “to do” list? Find her old friends that are just as horny as she is. This is one issue Rebecca doesn’t want any of her fans to miss. 24-page full color comic book.
